cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this code, please cite both this repository and the original MT-Bench paper."
type: software
title: "MT-Bench Reproduction"
abstract: >
  A reproduction of the NeurIPS 2023 paper "Judging LLM-as-a-Judge with
  MT-Bench and Chatbot Arena". Reimplements the full evaluation pipeline
  (single-answer grading, pairwise comparison, reference-guided grading)
  as a self-contained Python package, and extends the original work with
  a Judge Scaling Law experiment (Qwen2.5 7B/14B/32B) and a
  discriminability-based gap analysis.
authors:
